             England fullback Ashley Cole wants to
quit Chelsea and join former Blues coach Jose Mourinho at Real
Madrid, the News of the World reported, citing a source it
didnâ€™t identify.  
 The 29-year-old told current Chelsea coach Carlo Ancelotti
in a 20 minute conversation that he feels he needs to leave, the
